# Highlight Selection – BMAD Approach

This project implements the same highlight selection feature using a BMAD (agent-driven AI workflow).

The implementation was generated through an iterative AI-assisted workflow.

This repository is part of the Generative AI Evangelist assignment.

## Scoring Rules

Base scores:

- goal = 4
- assist = 3
- card = 1

Preference boosts:

- favorite player +8
- favorite team +5

## Architecture

Events Input  
↓  
Scoring Engine  
↓  
Filtering  
↓  
Sorting  
↓  
Highlights Output  

## Run

```bash
python src/highlight_selector.py
